Red Hot Chili Peppers - Californication (1999)
Today I‘m joining @thelegendsofmusic and @vinylgoneviral for #rhcpappreciationday! 🥳 Definitely a band worth celebrating! For this occasion I chose „Californication“, because it was the very first RHCP album I owned as a kid, and I still love it a lot; especially because of „Scar Tissue“ 💙. And on this rainy day over here in Germany, this record brings back the summer vibes :).
Another band I wished I would have seen live! 

